00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:57,870
Better mind?

547
00:38:58,620 --> 00:39:01,420
Well, I was trying to be modest.

548
00:39:01,790 --> 00:39:03,710
A less busy mind.

549
00:39:04,130 --> 00:39:05,420
Yours.

