00:41:23,640 --> 00:41:24,930
On what basis?

587
00:41:25,100 --> 00:41:26,640
I flipped a coin.

588
00:41:32,780 --> 00:41:34,690
It says rye... I said no rye, man.

589
00:41:37,280 --> 00:41:40,070
Hey, rookie, lose the helmet.
