00:43:47,870 --> 00:43:50,370
- Thank you.
- That'll slow them down.

610
00:43:51,040 --> 00:43:52,080
Move back!

611
00:43:52,250 --> 00:43:54,920
All the way! Go! Sir, get back, please!

612
00:43:56,420 --> 00:43:58,000
They cut the fiber.

613
00:43:59,170 --> 00:44:00,260
Cell's working.

614
00:44:00,420 --> 00:44:01,760
For now.

615
00:44:07,430 --> 00:44:09,180
Get all these barriers
up. All of them up.

616
00:44:09,180 --> 00:44:11,100
No one gets in or out
of any of these streets.

617
00:44:11,270 --> 00:44:12,890
Where am I supposed to move it?

