00:44:13,060 --> 00:44:14,350
Back it up.

619
00:44:18,940 --> 00:44:21,150
All right, just stay
in your vehicle, okay?

620
00:44:27,700 --> 00:44:30,120
How much longer does the program need?

621
00:44:31,710 --> 00:44:32,870
Eight minutes.

622
00:44:34,460 --> 00:44:35,710
Time to go mobile.

623
00:44:35,880 --> 00:44:37,210
Everybody, up!

624
00:44:41,470 --> 00:44:42,840
You two, move!

625
00:44:45,680 --> 00:44:46,970
Thank you.

626
00:44:47,930 --> 00:44:49,390
Steady.

627
00:44:58,110 --> 00:44:59,480
Steady.

628
00:45:07,410 --> 00:45:08,450
I've got something.

629
00:45:09,580 --> 00:45:12,080
Hold your fire, they've got hostages.

630
00:45:12,250 --> 00:45:13,500
Hold your fire!

631
00:45:23,470 --> 00:45:24,970
Go, go!

632
00:45:34,690 --> 00:45:36,350
Please! Just let me go!

633
00:45:36,690 --> 00:45:39,310
Hey, please! Hey!

634
00:45:42,320 --> 00:45:43,740
Shoot the tires.

635
00:45:43,900 --> 00:45:45,360
There's no shot.

636
00:45:46,780 --> 00:45:49,910
Now back off. Back off,
they've got hostages.

