00:46:12,060 --> 00:46:13,140
What the hell was that?

641
00:46:13,310 --> 00:46:16,140
Oh, boy, you are in
for a show tonight, son.

642
00:46:21,650 --> 00:46:23,650
Please! Help, help, help!

643
00:46:41,500 --> 00:46:42,540
Sorry.

644
00:46:43,170 --> 00:46:46,460
Put that thing away before
you hurt yourself. Get in!

645
00:46:46,630 --> 00:46:49,760
Let's go. You, get in the car.
