00:47:04,360 --> 00:47:07,070
Pull them in now. I'm gonna
do what Jim Gordon never could.

648
00:47:07,240 --> 00:47:10,450
- What's that?
- I'm gonna take down the Batman.

649
00:47:11,720 --> 00:47:13,660
four suspects are carrying two hostages

