00:47:17,660 --> 00:47:19,330
Scott, dead center of your screen.

653
00:47:19,500 --> 00:47:21,920
- What do you see?
- I see Batman.

654
00:47:22,080 --> 00:47:22,980
Hard to believe,

655
00:47:22,980 --> 00:47:25,960
but the suspects are now
being pursued by what appears

