00:51:12,150 --> 00:51:15,570
Bane says the Batman interfered,
but the task was accomplished.

681
00:51:15,730 --> 00:51:17,360
What about the men they arrested?

682
00:51:17,530 --> 00:51:21,610
He said, and I quote, "They
