683
00:51:22,820 --> 00:51:25,120
Where does he find these guys?

684
00:51:26,700 --> 00:51:28,450
Open the champagne.

685
00:51:30,500 --> 00:51:33,000
And can we get some girls in here?

686
00:51:33,170 --> 00:51:34,590
Careful what you wish for.

687
00:51:45,600 --> 00:51:46,930
Cat got your tongue?

688
00:51:47,100 --> 00:51:48,310
You dumb bitch.

689
00:51:48,480 --> 00:51:50,560
Nobody ever accused me of being dumb.

690
00:51:50,730 --> 00:51:53,650
You're dumb for coming here tonight.

691
00:51:55,070 --> 00:51:56,730
I want what you owe me.

692
00:51:58,570 --> 00:52:00,490
Want doesn't get.

693
00:52:00,990 --> 00:52:05,030
Nice outfit. Those heels
