00:52:14,130 --> 00:52:17,340
The ultimate tool for a
master thief with a record.

699
00:52:18,090 --> 00:52:19,630
Hold it right there!

700
00:52:33,150 --> 00:52:34,190
Where is it?

701
00:52:34,730 --> 00:52:36,310
The clean slate?

702
00:52:36,480 --> 00:52:39,110
Where you type in someone's
name, date of birth

703
00:52:39,280 --> 00:52:43,450
in a few minutes they're gone
