704
00:52:43,990 --> 00:52:46,780
- Sound a little too good to be true?
- You're lying!

705
00:52:46,950 --> 00:52:49,540
Rykin Data took it to prototype stage.

706
00:52:49,700 --> 00:52:51,660
That's why I bought them.

707
00:52:52,580 --> 00:52:54,460
But they had nothing.

708
00:52:54,880 --> 00:52:56,580
It was a gangland myth.

709
00:53:07,930 --> 00:53:09,100
Stay back!

710
00:53:12,480 --> 00:53:14,100
I'm not bluffing!

711
00:53:15,020 --> 00:53:16,400
