into cars with strange men.

716
00:54:01,690 --> 00:54:02,730
This isn't a car.

717
00:54:52,870 --> 00:54:54,450
See you around.

718
00:54:55,450 --> 00:54:56,580
You're welcome.

719
00:54:56,960 --> 00:54:58,330
I had it under control.

720
00:54:58,500 --> 00:54:59,830
Those weren't street thugs.

721
